  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want discover screens to look pretty like in the design so that using discover is a delight.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: There are a number of discrepancies between the design and Discover. The goal of this issue is to capture the main ones for: Main Screen.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31393637-8060e1e2-addc-11e7-9782-d6b1652c4a16.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31393648-8534646e-addc-11e7-879a-22109155acdc.png)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\niOS only for now - Android screens to come.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31548194-52bce600-b02a-11e7-8dd4-960279120516.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31548198-56f9b8c4-b02a-11e7-8fed-8c0cf749c09e.png)\r\n\r\nAndroid (Oct 16)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31607758-e1c8edae-b26d-11e7-8c30-1286e09f4445.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31607772-ed80bd8e-b26d-11e7-865a-72932a99c361.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### List of things to fix (non-exhaustive)\r\n- [x] Recent statuses etc headers font lowercase\r\n- [x] Status font margin to below\r\n- [x] Name Icon not centered for cards\r\n- [x] Popular hashtag grey margins bottom\r\n- [x] DApps icon size - make bigger and remove `...`\r\n- [x] DApps tighter horizontal margin (requires https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/2116)\r\n- [x] DApps get rid of scrollbar\r\n- [x] DApps grey margin to public chats\r\n- [x] Public chats padding left\r\n\r\n### Must have\r\n\r\n- [ ] TEST -> Chat button either missing or wrong color&corners (Android saw on Goran's screen - will be fixed in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/2119)\r\n- [ ] TEST -> Public chats scroll to end last one covered by menu bar (hm, can't reproduce? - @annadanchenko?)\r\n- [ ] Right font size for contact username is 14\r\n- [ ] tap on the number of popular hashtags  -> popup ...\r\n- [x] Popular hashtags - card has borders (at least in ios) should have no borders (lines)\r\n- [x] All for DApps should be blue, now grey\r\n\r\n### Nice have\r\n- [ ] Chat button should have margin 12 px from the bottom of the card\r\n- [ ] Too wide top margin toolbar (16 vs 8 I think)\r\n- [ ] Size of cards should be equal (3 lines can fit) on Recent statuses\r\n- [ ] Public chats - change title of 3 chats  to #status #testing #163 \r\n- [ ] Popular hashtags font weight\r\n- [ ] DApps and Public chats bg header bg color ( @denis-sharypin playing around with alt designs so hold)\r\n- [ ] Recent statuses horizontal line header\r\n- [ ] TEST -> check UI checklist\r\n\r\n### MISC\r\n@oskarth - [ ] IGNORE Android - Dapps preview not shown (?)",
